Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝得好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪丝 怎么能把人质给杀了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你怎么自说自话就死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…克罗里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正人质还有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 冯也来喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也稍微控制下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还算是贵族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 活得那么一本正经有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 克罗里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也稍微活得正经点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 克罗里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这次的事件您怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于连这名古屋也遭到人类的围攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说琪丝 稍微过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想看看这个人类的武器和吸血鬼的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪个比较强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克罗里大人用的话 不管什么都很强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题的关键不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个…我只是觉得人类变强的速度实在太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施加了鬼的诅咒 用来击杀吸血鬼的武器吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 实际上是有人把我们的情报泄露给人类了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说我们之中有叛徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是位居上位之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所见 伤口完全没有复原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个也要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上替您处理伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想喝的话来喝也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…克罗里大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是刚喝完人类的血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不公平 不公平 不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场大规模的战争是不是有谁在幕后操纵着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克鲁鲁·采佩西呢 还是费里德·巴特利…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然觉得人类应该不是幕后黑手才对 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 要在这里待机到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到其他部队来集合为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时间集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,14时20分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在几点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一濑中校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到20分之前在这待机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的队伍是三小队15人执行任务的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多同伴牺牲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话怎么回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的队伍毫发无伤吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为队长很优秀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧 柊筱娅队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 突然把话甩给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你们能活着回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里由我们守着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的新人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我记得名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没记住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明之前还说什么要我好好记住敌人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是百夜优一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 百夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就听你的话 我们稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒备就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…任务中会有同伴牺牲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 同伴会有牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是战场…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 要珍惜每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相守护着对方一起前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在那悠闲地晒什么太阳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必是完成任务了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 你那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新人们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有拖你后腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之前预想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们表现很出色 完全不像是新人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别蹬鼻子上脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有八位同伴牺牲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校 真的非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去同伴我有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…全部都是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能活着回来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣海 其他的部队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不等其他的部队了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继续执行下一个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个任务？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击市政厅内三只吸血鬼贵族的九个部队全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十五人被当成了人质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的作战还需要大量的人员参与
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以由我们去将那些贵族杀死 救出同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校 请让我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想帮中校…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战场上掉眼泪的家伙会拖后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们救出人质后 在机场再集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你来向回到这里的其他部队传达这个指令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 出发吧小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说既然知道是陷阱就不该去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 不得不去不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在失去这些部队的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赋予我们的任务就完成不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 你有什么不满
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没说有不满
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴被屠杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是最害怕这种事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 想问问你要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会有人牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使知道这点 仍然会陷入自责不正是你的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些精锐部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是 相信他们慢慢等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相原队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过把目标全部消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真的太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校会去机场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那里集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 行动代号284
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 行动代号284
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在受到拷问逼供前先服毒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嘴里放置了毒药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能让你死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事情要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我装死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然其他吸血鬼会发现你还活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好回答我问题的话就放你一马 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识一个叫百夜优一郎的人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛在说你认识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想活命的话就全部说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会出卖同伴的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴 你们才不是小优的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 到底是想干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人类也和他们一样 自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么这些家伙要自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子有病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是吸血鬼被杀的痕迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管辖这片区域的是卢考勒·威士卡大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是不可能和贵族抗衡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉库斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷涅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下的同胞全都被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅鲁·斯特伐诺大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我们找遍了也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 事情变得怪异起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先转移吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克罗里大人应该在市政厅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再动的话我就杀了这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢 米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住她 问出情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了也不在乎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了的话也怪米迦自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我自己想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百夜优一郎 现在正赶往市政厅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在如果你们去了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全都会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你把我们的新人称为「小优」的这件事上赌一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所知道的就只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做你懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的其他同伴都自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你却贪生怕死地想要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么想活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快把你同伴的所在地招出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击了这里的那些家伙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了 能不杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本帝鬼军第二中队…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在东山公园
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正想要去袭击植物园
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划杀掉赛因·林都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是 竟然不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是第十七位始祖大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连贵族大人的姓名和所在地都暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来事情变得麻烦起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道了如果不去的话 之后会很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 好远的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死的话自己去死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果自杀的话 我刚才所说的情报就会遭到怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若是由你动手杀了我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点就丢下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个人类也带走 米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经没有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她把其他的情报也招出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正到最后你们还是会杀了我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 杀掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家畜们的情报根本无足轻重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这些人类对组织的疯狂信仰真是让人有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本帝鬼军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是个很不简单的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 人类只要一聚在一起就不会搞出什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先去植物园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让第十七位始祖大人被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类所说的话 不能全部相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我五名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一 我去市政厅查看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那边就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你保护了小优吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在利用他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往市政厅查看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就来 小优
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是天转阴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是袭击的好天气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 终结的炽天使
